first_para: Rachel Jane Reeves (born 13 February 1979) is a British Labour Party politician and an economist. She has served as the Member of Parliament for Leeds West since 2010.

full.extract:
Rachel Jane Reeves (born 13 February 1979) is a British Labour Party politician and an economist. She has served as the Member of Parliament for Leeds West since 2010.
Reeves is the current Shadow Secretary of State for Work and Pensions.
full.title: Rachel Reeves
